 you have <strong>oily-to-combo skin<\/strong> or in warmer climates and seasons, facial oils can be used in replacement of a moisturizer.<\/p><p>If you have <strong>normal-to-dry skin <\/strong>or in colder climates and seasons, try layering face oils after moisturizers for extra moisture and to seal in all of the skincare that comes before!<\/p><p><\/p>","open_by_default":false,"icon":"none","icon_advanced_settings":false,"icon_height_desktop":28,"icon_height":27,"icon_margin_desktop":0,"icon_margin":0}},"collapsible_tab_cYxEtN":{"type":"collapsible_tab","settings":{"heading":"Can Orchid be used all over your body?","content":"<p>We recommend using Orchid oil primarily for your face and neck. If you are looking for a body oil, try our NEW NOVA Body Oil.<\/p>","open_by_default":false,"icon":"none","icon_advanced_settings":false,"icon_height_desktop":28,"icon_height":27,"icon_margin_desktop":0,"icon_margin":0}},"collapsible_tab_VXtATz":{"type":"collapsible_tab","settings":{"heading":"Can I use the oil with my regular moisturizer?","content":"<p>You can use this as a moisturizer or layer on top of your moisturizing cream to lock moisture in.<\/p>","open_by_default":false,"icon":"none","icon_advanced_settings":false,"icon_height_desktop":28,"icon_height":27,"icon_margin_desktop":0,"icon_margin":0}},"collapsible_tab_iHcQeH":{"type":"collapsible_tab","settings":{"heading":"Can I use the oil morning and night?","content":"<p><strong>Yes. You can use the oil both morning and night.<\/strong>Apply a few drops to clean, slightly damp skin. In the morning, follow with sunscreen. In the evening, use it as the final step in your routine to help lock in moisture overnight.<\/p>","open_by_default":false,"icon":"none","icon_advanced_settings":false,"icon_height_desktop":28,"icon_height":27,"icon_margin_desktop":0,"icon_margin":0}},"collapsible_tab_DR34Br":{"type":"collapsible_tab","settings":{"heading":"Is this oil suitable for all skin types?","content":"<p>Yes, the formula is d